##Wuhan true dictation: This year, how do I live?

Micro-signal Zhenghedao

Features introduced by Zhenghe Island, a high-end social networking platform focused on entrepreneurs.

During the special period, Wuhan has become a city where people all over the country are concerned and pray for good fortune. What was the real life of the people of Wuhan after the city closure?

Zhenghe island has launched a special column, "Ye Qing: My n day in Wuhan Epidemic Area" , since January 26. Ye Qing, a resident of Wuhan for 40 years, is a scholar and official. For a period of time, he would write down his own experiences and observations of Wuhan, and he would go out to the streets and supermarkets to get first-hand information.

This will be a valuable piece of historical material. Thanks to him, we can feel the Wuhan epidemic more vividly. Let's Cheer for Wuhan Together!

Ye Qing, a professor at Zhongnan University of Economics and Law and deputy director of the Hubei Provincial Bureau of Statistics, is next door to blue island

Source: Zhenghe Island (ID: Zhenghedao)

"stability and order" in Wuhan City

January 26, the second day of the Lunar New Year, the 4th day of the city closure in Wuhan, drizzle.

In terms of national data, as of 2400 hours on 26 January, the National Health Commission had received a total of 2,744 confirmed cases from 30 provinces (autonomous regions and municipalities) , 461 severe cases and 80 cumulative deaths (24 new deaths) , 51 cases were cured and 5794 cases were suspected.

My general feeling is that it's stable and orderly.

This is a rare "stability" , from several central committee meetings.

On January 22, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan visited front line defense and control personnel in Wuhan.

On January 25, the first day of the Lunar New Year, the Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China held a meeting and the Party Central Committee set up a leading group to deal with the epidemic.

On January 26, Premier of the State Council and head of the COVID-19 chaired a meeting of the leading group.

On January 22, Vice Premier Sun Chunlan visited front line defense and control personnel in Wuhan.

On January 25, the first day of the Lunar New Year, the Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China held a meeting and the Party Central Committee set up a leading group to deal with the epidemic.

On January 26, Premier of the State Council and head of the COVID-19 chaired a meeting of the leading group.

After these investigations and meetings, a series of favorable measures have been put forward, and a large number of experts and materials have been arranged to go to Wuhan. The latest figures are more than 2,000 medical personnel and more than a million tons of supplies. These numbers, it is believed, are increasing every day.

However, the problem now is that Hubei is an epidemic area, Wuhan is a serious epidemic area, Hubei prefecture-level city how to do? In the video at night, the Shandong medical team was seen arriving in Huanggang. I suggest that the State Council can issue a regulation, so that the conditions of the provinces, cities and districts to send medical teams to support a city.

Japan supports a batch of masks in Wuhan, which are airlifted from Japan to Chengdu and then transported by road from Chengdu to Wuhan. We can get into Ensch and distribute some masks and other supplies along the way. So we don't have to reroute it. That's the social and public opinion message I'm going to deliver today.

Order, in the form of:

First, the market supply is stable, adequate supply of vegetable food. Hubei not only increased the supply of local vegetables, but also Chongqing, northeast, Inner Mongolia and other places of Chinese cabbage, potatoes, etc. also shipped to Wuhan.

On the 26th, a reporter from the People's Daily visited various supermarkets. See Wuhan Zhongshang Parity Supermarket East Lake Shop, two-storey shops are in normal business, shopping malls, many people wearing masks in shopping. There is an adequate supply of eggs, vegetables and other daily necessities. A packet of shredded beans, 13 yuan; a packet of brown sugar, 15.50 yuan.

Hongshan Zhuodao Spring Street will be the jurisdiction of the 16 supermarket business hours out, sent to the residents of Wechat group to facilitate shopping. It is understood that most supermarkets open at the same time as the Spring Festival in previous years.

In order to understand the real situation, 8:00 pm, I specifically around the neighborhood to see. There are two supermarkets, big and small, still open.

The shelves are full of food and vegetables. The price has not changed much, except for a slight increase in the price of vegetables.

Second, the road traffic is scarce, we do not go out.

We live in this community are south-central financial university teachers, due to an early holiday, only one-third of the home lights. There is also a Lanzhou Noodle restaurant with lights on, but not open for business. I guess I can't go back, so I have to stay in Wuhan for the Spring Festival.

The taxi on duty in the community lit up the lights of the empty car, quietly waiting for people in need.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
According to media reports, the government has commandeered 6,000 taxis, some online taxis and more than 300 buses, and is orderly picking up and dropping off patients, medical staff and those in need, or going out to work.

It should be added that the "car closure" in Wuhan is relative. Whoever receives a mobile phone message can not drive on the street, but did not receive a mobile phone message from the traffic control department, or can go on the street. However, on the bridge to measure the temperature, no one will casually cross the river.

That is to say, there may be suspected patients in the home, by special taxis, ride-hailing cars, the drivers of these vehicles have protective equipment, some even goggles, protective clothing have, every time the delivery of disinfection once. Well, that's very considerate of you.

Third, good news is constantly coming through Wechat. It's getting more and more reassuring.

Shanghai Medical Treatment Expert Group leader Professor Zhang Wenhong believes that the main battle to control new coronavirus infection in Wuhan should be completed within 1 month, 2 months into the end.

Wuhan University Zhongnan Hospital Professor of Infection, well-known AIDS prevention and treatment experts Gui Xien has been more than 80 years old, but has been struggling in the research front line. He thinks:

Although the current situation is very serious, governments at all levels are attaching great importance to this issue, and the current means of examination and treatment are much more advanced than before, so the epidemic can be completely controlled. The spread of new pneumonia is mainly through the spread of droplets, so as long as careful prevention is appropriate, completely can be controlled!

Professor Guissian believes that although the numbers are getting bigger every day, they will fall rapidly once they are brought under control. Therefore, he predicted that the Wuhan epidemic may be reduced before the Fifteenth Day of the first lunar month.

Professor Gui's words, in fact, are also the words of all of us in Wuhan, which are well-founded. A lot of things are easier when the boss takes them seriously. That's where confidence comes from.

Scientists and doctors around the world are working on a vaccine and a cure for the new coronavirus pneumonia, a race between science and the virus.

Takatomi, director of the Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention and a member of the high level expert panel of the National Health Commission, said at a news conference held by the state news agency:

You know it takes a long, long time to develop a vaccine. But from what we know about SARS, about this virus, I can pat myself on the chest and say, this vaccine is going to work! But to respect the laws of nature, it requires step-by-step experimentation.

At the same time as the construction of the Vulcan Mountain Hospital in Caidian District, the construction of the Thor Mountain Hospital in Jiangxia District opened on the 26th. What kind of name is that? It turned out that I was deceived, there is no such place name, is the Wuhan people themselves. According to the I ching, fire, thunder are grams of poison, no wonder there is a car called "Lexus" , that is, "Lake SARS. ". Wuhan people are so humorous!

Fourth, the medical force in Wuhan has been greatly enhanced.

The force medical unit has taken over a number of designated hospitals and has added new treatment centres.

Let me give you an example. On the 26th, the Inpatient Department of the Central War Zone General Hospital is vacating the existing inpatient building, setting the internal medicine inpatient department as a special area for new pneumonia. After adjustment, the zone will increase to more than 500 beds, is applying to become Wuhan to fight new pneumonia another fixed point hospital.

And on the morning of the 23rd, when I passed the big hospital at the corner of the street, I found why the hospital was so quiet. Now, this will be the new battleground.

Wuhan is finally "out of loneliness" . From single-player (city) to co-operation.

Fifthly, the days when rumors were flying all over the place were passing away.

On January 25, the Wechat Security Center released a notice on the special treatment of rumors related to COVID-19 pneumonia. WECHAT will set up a "COVID-19 pneumonia"-related rumors to clear up the special, continue to strengthen the crackdown, tencent more real-time Verification Platform will also be Covid-19 pneumonia-related information refuted rumors; Users are also welcome to complain about rumors.

WECHAT SECURITY CENTER WARNS:

In the face of the epidemic situation, we should keep calm and rational. The majority of users should learn about the epidemic situation from disease control or medical institutions and authoritative news media. The relevant epidemic prevention information should be published on the official websites of the provincial and municipal health committees. Do not listen to rumors, increase the unnecessary psychological burden, do not believe rumors do not spread rumors, improve vigilance and recognition ability.

No wonder there were fewer rumors on the 26th.

Still, it's hard to get rid of.

"The Wuhan Red Cross charges the Shanghai medical team 6% to 8% for donated services, otherwise they will refuse to accept medical supplies such as protective clothing, " said screenshots posted on the Internet Sunday, and "the Wuhan Red Cross cut off all private independent ways, all materials unified deployment. ". Many netizens demanded a public explanation from the Wuhan Red Cross Society.

In the early hours of January 27, the Red Cross Society of Wuhan posted a statement on its official Weibo account@universal fraternity  universal love in Wuhan saying that there were no charges in any workflow.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At first it was hard to see the news. To see the message of refuting rumors, only to be relieved. But it's been hard for hours. So, a rumor is an artificial virus.

In order for people to work together, please don't spread unverified information.

Of course, the problem that some netizen reflects, also be worth taking seriously. For example, why don't big supermarkets have temperature measuring devices? The waiting time for payment is too long, we should improve it.

Sixth, universities have said to delay the start of school, so that students at home to read more, less door-to-door.

The Ministry of Education issued a special notice on the 23rd, requesting colleges and universities (not only in Wuhan) to pay close attention to the development of the epidemic at all times, and to make scientific research and judgment in advance for the spring start of the semester, and to make appropriate adjustments to teaching arrangements and work when necessary.

As of January 26, a total of 18 universities in Hubei Province had issued a notice to delay their spring enrollment.

I posted on my wechat account, recommending six books recommended by Ren Zhengfei. Ren Zhengfei, the founder of Huawei, is an "expert" in reading. As the spiritual leader of Huawei, Ren always insists on reading and uses the fragmented time to study.

Does the Wuhan Person Of the field live well?

You can imagine how hard it must have been. From the 26th, the topic of how Wuhan People Go home flooded wechat. The people of Wuhan in Han Dynasty will certainly understand the people of Wuhan outside. Yesterday, I said to be kind to Wuhan people. Now it seems that this is a matter that needs the help of the people of the whole country.

The mayor said that 5 million people left Wuhan and 9 million remained in Wuhan.

Of the 5M people who left Wuhan, two things happened:

Part of the work in Wuhan, home for the New Year. This part of the people is at least living at home, the cost of New Year is also lower, although will encounter all sorts of censure.

The other part is to go out travel completely according to plan, make contribution for national tourism economy. Postponing their return to Wuhan would add a lot to their costs. A friend called me, said in Sanya, two houses, a room a day 1600 yuan, can not stand.

You can't see the sights, you can't stay in a hotel, what can you do?

Yunnan, Shanghai, Guangdong and other places issued regulations, the Wuhan people concentrated in a number of hotels, to facilitate "monitoring. ".

The governor of Yunnan Province, a fellow-townsman from Wuhan, moved the fastest, and requested that by 18 o'clock on the 26th, in principle each city and state should decide on a hotel to admit Wuhan people.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In addition, alumni of my alma mater are on the move (I am a postdoctoral fellow at the Wuhan University School of Business) .

On the evening of January 26, the website of the Wuhan University on New Pneumonia Prevention and control updated a message of "convenient service" :

For Hubei residents who are temporarily unable to return to their hometown and have nowhere else to go, please look for Wuhan University, an alumni company, to accept Hubei guests. These hotels include my mansion, Mrs. Bailey, Jin Cheng, Yicheng, Yishang Plus, Yishang, Feng. Attitude, Perlman, Platon, inmo, city convenience, road.

At present, the group has more than 2,500 hotels (including planning) , more than 200,000 rooms, distributed in more than 200 cities around the world.

Did Not expect that the key time Wuhan Alumni can also play this special role.

State Council General Office Notice: The 2020 Spring Festival holiday will be extended to February 2(Sunday, the ninth day of the first lunar month) , and work will start on February 3(Monday) .

I wonder if these Wuhan people can come back on time?

Things with our family

The kind we take twice a day in our house, in our ears. It was supposed to be for kids, but we used it early. I guess the kids are okay with it. It is absolutely necessary to have a smart thermometer in the house.

Mrs Lee made a video of her cooking and showed it to the students, hoping to increase their nutrition. My doctoral students, master's students, like a family. I teach them knowledge, Madam teaches them to cook, division of Labor is clear.

Not Seeing each other is also a kind of care, is also a kind of love.

The 26th passed. Stable and orderly, more and more thin, united, full of hope.

I hope the 27th will be better. I hope the people in Hubei are better.
